Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:13.48,default,,0,0,0,,It's small but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:15.63,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:17.66,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:39.47,default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:40.14,default,,0,0,0,,I'm Noyuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.57,default,,0,0,0,,I'm the manager of Nogizaka46.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.33,default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly took it with my cell phone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.62,default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to make a video, but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:58.20,default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what to use, but I didn't know how to use it like this, and I didn't know the meaning of my birthday, so I was told to speak casually today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.74,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a talent for the time being
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.91,default,,0,0,0,,This is Nagizaka46
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:26.60,default,,0,0,0,,I would like to introduce a video taken by our manager, but I am alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.05,default,,0,0,0,,Nanaka-san from Senpai also came.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:31.26,default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Nonaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.03,default,,0,0,0,,Konnichiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.93,default,,0,0,0,,Well, today I happened to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:49.72,default,,0,0,0,,When I went to the office, I learned that there was a narration, and when the scene was over, I was allowed to sit here, but let's leave that aside and watch the behind-the-scenes video of the handshake meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:50.51,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:17.65,default,,0,0,0,,This is what the backstage looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:27.05,default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to Overture, other than the well-known site, Haruto Farm, everyone's tension is maxed out and it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.79,default,,0,0,0,,Minami is pushing Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:33.08,default,,0,0,0,,That was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.91,default,,0,0,0,,Nanami is cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.25,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.17,default,,0,0,0,,I took the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.86,default,,0,0,0,,For me, for someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.18,default,,0,0,0,,I'm singing in the back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.24,default,,0,0,0,,There are four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.41,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.91,default,,0,0,0,,It's not about singing and dancing, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.61,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.95,default,,0,0,0,,What are you singing at the end of the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:30.45,default,,0,0,0,,The people who wanted to sing at the end of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:35.47,default,,0,0,0,,It's just that the larynx is a little rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.37,default,,0,0,0,,But it takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:41.19,default,,0,0,0,,Your face is great too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.95,default,,0,0,0,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:45.87,default,,0,0,0,,Hohohohoho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.35,default,,0,0,0,,On the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.30,default,,0,0,0,,Marika Shiraishi and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:54.42,default,,0,0,0,,Kikimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.09,default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.16,default,,0,0,0,,This side looks like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:03.19,default,,0,0,0,,People usually dance when they're in a bad mood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.19,default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're not in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.37,default,,0,0,0,,dance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:12.85,default,,0,0,0,,We are having fun and having fun behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:06.23,default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people who like songs that they haven't done before, so everyone does it seriously like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.77,default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.00,default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:11.90,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:13.40,default,,0,0,0,,It looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:20.59,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it hurts. I ran into the field and was about to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.46,default,,0,0,0,,And then we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.46,default,,0,0,0,,Have a good trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:39.65,default,,0,0,0,,This is how the actual handshake looks like, but who took this? Koi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.65,default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.65,default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.40,default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:49.59,default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.21,default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.79,default,,0,0,0,,The two people who love cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:54.77,default,,0,0,0,,The face of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.20,default,,0,0,0,,They will come in for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.10,default,,0,0,0,,This is the one I took.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.32,default,,0,0,0,,This is Chie-chan's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.56,default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.56,default,,0,0,0,,Chi-chan and Ami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.41,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.00,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.93,default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't Ami here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:25.33,default,,0,0,0,,The old lady from the summer tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.79,default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.19,default,,0,0,0,,This is Nanami-san in the summer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:37.33,default,,0,0,0,,She's practicing for the members
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.71,default,,0,0,0,,Can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.41,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.92,default,,0,0,0,,I like this a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.85,default,,0,0,0,,It's a refreshing dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.54,default,,0,0,0,,I can feel the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:59.15,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is Kawagopi trying to shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:00.89,default,,0,0,0,,This is from a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:03.09,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:02.64,default,,0,0,0,,A little?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.37,default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.37,default,,0,0,0,,I'm transforming into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.53,default,,0,0,0,,Cargo P.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.29,default,,0,0,0,,I'm transforming into Cargo P.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.73,default,,0,0,0,,Konno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:13.11,default,,0,0,0,,Konno-san is leading the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:14.75,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.90,default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:17.90,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.65,default,,0,0,0,,You can access it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:28.78,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.13,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.57,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.55,default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.15,default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.86,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.77,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.19,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.57,default,,0,0,0,,There was a face-shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.57,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:29.57,default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it a member?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.57,default,,0,0,0,,Was it a member?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:31.57,default,,0,0,0,,A member was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:32.57,default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:35.53,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:41.39,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.51,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.56,default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for the live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.02,default,,0,0,0,,Koi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.02,default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any memories of the concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.88,default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:11:01.97,default,,0,0,0,,There might be a lot, but it's a place where all the members have a sense of unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:04.21,default,,0,0,0,,It's a good memory every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:05.39,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:06.64,default,,0,0,0,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.31,default,,0,0,0,,Jingu from last year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.83,default,,0,0,0,,It's already nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:14.71,default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's been a year yet, but it's nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:16.27,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.82,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:38.31,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:45.79,default,,0,0,0,,This person is getting closer and closer to the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.05,default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.05,default,,0,0,0,,But it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:52.05,default,,0,0,0,,It was exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.14,default,,0,0,0,,Good luck everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:12:01.91,default,,0,0,0,,This is from our national tour in 2013, and when I was listening to Kana,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:04.21,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:08.73,default,,0,0,0,,It's like a picture of Marika trying to make a fool out of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.86,default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.01,default,,0,0,0,,Nanami and Renarin are smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.11,default,,0,0,0,,That's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.11,default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:20.11,default,,0,0,0,,The first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.11,default,,0,0,0,,Your face is so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.11,default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll tell Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:28.25,default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to answer to Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.68,default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was able to do it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:32.88,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.96,default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.96,default,,0,0,0,,It's so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:41.36,default,,0,0,0,,This happy look is also nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.36,default,,0,0,0,,Is this a get-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:44.66,default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.36,default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.03,default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:50.32,default,,0,0,0,,The one where Kazumi got injured and couldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:54.10,default,,0,0,0,,The one where Kazumi got injured and couldn't come out of the girls' room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.01,default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.72,default,,0,0,0,,This is how we do our concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.53,default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of drama behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.75,default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.91,default,,0,0,0,,It's so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:13.20,default,,0,0,0,,I put a lot of thought into the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.06,default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.97,default,,0,0,0,,I was worried but I couldn't go out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.68,default,,0,0,0,,Kazumi-san, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:28.88,default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be on stage for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.07,default,,0,0,0,,I was so frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.88,default,,0,0,0,,My hair is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:34.93,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:35.83,default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.41,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:39.06,default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.30,default,,0,0,0,,At times like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:14:14.62,default,,0,0,0,,Translated by Releska
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.53,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.11,default,,0,0,0,,The way she speaks and the way she talks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:56.51,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:57.33,default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:03.72,default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is stay by her side and encourage her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:06.26,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.54,default,,0,0,0,,The concert tour too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.22,default,,0,0,0,,There are probably only a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.59,default,,0,0,0,,The person himself is also very prominent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.28,default,,0,0,0,,It was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.55,default,,0,0,0,,It was hard for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:19.25,default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:35.51,default,,0,0,0,,This is a picture of Hashimoto's rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:37.61,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:44.70,default,,0,0,0,,What are the two of them doing behind the scenes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:50.87,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're doing, but I didn't notice you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.57,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I was beaten by Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.92,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.24,default,,0,0,0,,The overreaction is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.41,default,,0,0,0,,It's like a major leaguer because he's chewing gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:11.51,default,,0,0,0,,Major leaguer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:18.13,default,,0,0,0,,This is a practice video of the Nogidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.83,default,,0,0,0,,Can you play 8 beats?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.17,default,,0,0,0,,I want to try this angle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.65,default,,0,0,0,,Just like that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:48.51,default,,0,0,0,,It didn't change much, but it was the limit of my height.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.86,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:14.79,default,,0,0,0,,Waki-Ai-Ai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.02,default,,0,0,0,,Nogidan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.70,default,,0,0,0,,I practiced a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:19.92,default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:30.97,default,,0,0,0,,I was so busy that I couldn't find the time to do it, so everyone was so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:35.23,default,,0,0,0,,But it was so much fun to be able to do it all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.33,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
