Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.68,0:41:01.68,default,,0,0,0,,The one from 7-Eleven?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.68,0:41:03.68,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the one from the commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.70,0:41:06.70,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.72,0:41:08.72,default,,0,0,0,,7-Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.72,0:41:10.72,default,,0,0,0,,7-Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.72,0:41:12.72,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.72,0:41:14.72,default,,0,0,0,,Okay okay
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.72,0:41:16.72,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.17,0:41:19.51,default,,0,0,0,,This tree is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.36,0:41:24.22,default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.33,0:41:28.33,default,,0,0,0,,A video?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.80,0:41:30.80,default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.30,0:41:33.30,default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.30,0:41:38.30,default,,0,0,0,,From now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.53,0:41:40.53,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.53,0:41:44.53,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say my lines one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.53,0:41:46.53,default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish it in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.68,0:41:49.94,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home at 9 o'clock today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.72,0:41:51.50,default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.35,0:41:54.35,default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.35,0:41:56.35,default,,0,0,0,,This is my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.73,0:41:57.23,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.41,0:41:58.67,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.67,0:42:00.59,default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the big day!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.31,0:42:02.89,default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.90,0:42:04.64,default,,0,0,0,,16 days
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.47,0:42:07.47,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.08,0:42:08.08,default,,0,0,0,,Go for it! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.08,0:42:10.08,default,,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.08,0:42:17.08,default,,0,0,0,,This is from Teiichi's rehearsal on the day before the actual show.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.08,0:42:25.08,default,,0,0,0,,He pulled Inoue out of the stage and did the commercial shoot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.96,0:42:28.46,default,,0,0,0,,This is also a very recent video.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.46,0:42:32.12,default,,0,0,0,,It's the Sayuringo Corps behind the scenes of Nogibingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.38,0:42:34.44,default,,0,0,0,,Koi-chan, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.85,0:42:37.85,default,,0,0,0,,Are you filming while rotating with Matsumura and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.85,0:42:40.01,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.66,0:42:43.06,default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.23,0:42:43.73,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.97,0:42:45.49,default,,0,0,0,,It's just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.04,0:42:52.86,default,,0,0,0,,The captain of the Sayuringo Corps and the vice-captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.09,0:42:54.11,default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.33,0:42:55.21,default,,0,0,0,,Kanji
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.00,0:42:58.00,default,,0,0,0,,It's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.00,0:43:00.00,default,,0,0,0,,It's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.08,0:43:08.08,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.72,0:43:09.04,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.18,0:43:09.68,default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.40,0:43:11.46,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.90,0:43:13.26,default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.98,0:43:23.12,default,,0,0,0,,I also bought a DVD of the song that I had a hard time listening to, so I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.49,0:43:25.49,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.77,0:43:26.77,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.53,0:43:28.25,default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.35,0:43:30.35,default,,0,0,0,,I'm a real Umamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.35,0:43:32.35,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.35,0:43:34.35,default,,0,0,0,,Umamiko, Umamiko, Umamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.23,0:43:36.79,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.28,0:43:39.28,default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.28,0:43:41.28,default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.28,0:43:43.28,default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.28,0:43:45.28,default,,0,0,0,,I heard it from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.28,0:43:45.78,default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.92,0:43:47.92,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.78,0:43:49.78,default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Kuma and Ichi-san went back to their room?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.78,0:43:52.78,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they went back to their room.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.84,0:43:59.48,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.84,0:44:01.30,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.98,0:44:03.70,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.97,0:44:07.47,default,,0,0,0,,It's a weird face from the day I took it forcibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.61,0:44:09.93,default,,0,0,0,,It's almost the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.08,0:44:12.08,default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.08,0:44:14.08,default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.08,0:44:16.08,default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.08,0:44:18.08,default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.08,0:44:20.08,default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.08,0:44:22.08,default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.08,0:44:28.08,default,,0,0,0,,Shin-chan, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.28,0:44:34.32,default,,0,0,0,,This is what Maaya asked me to do
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.36,0:44:36.60,default,,0,0,0,,Facial exercise?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.83,0:44:37.33,default,,0,0,0,,It's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.63,0:44:38.45,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.62,0:44:42.46,default,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.77,0:44:46.77,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.39,0:44:49.39,default,,0,0,0,,Hold it with your hand like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.39,0:44:51.39,default,,0,0,0,,Basically, you can do it on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.77,0:44:55.85,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.85,0:44:59.35,default,,0,0,0,,But Maaya is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.09,0:45:02.35,default,,0,0,0,,The mood maker of the group is really kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.35,0:45:05.25,default,,0,0,0,,It's a healing Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.63,0:45:10.63,default,,0,0,0,,And this is Karin who can't open the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.01,0:45:11.87,default,,0,0,0,,Karin-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.17,0:45:16.17,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.17,0:45:18.17,default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a trick to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.17,0:45:20.17,default,,0,0,0,,It's a little difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.29,0:45:25.85,default,,0,0,0,,I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.49,0:45:29.49,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.41,0:45:33.17,default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a break now. Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.22,0:45:38.22,default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.49,0:45:40.65,default,,0,0,0,,I can see it! It's an art!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.61,0:45:44.21,default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.37,0:45:47.37,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for waking you up
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.36,0:45:52.76,default,,0,0,0,,lol
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.61,0:45:58.21,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.81,0:46:00.81,default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.81,0:46:04.81,default,,0,0,0,,It's really messy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.81,0:46:06.81,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.53,0:46:08.53,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.53,0:46:10.31,default,,0,0,0,,SOMBARU
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.43,0:46:15.43,default,,0,0,0,,This is also during the break in the middle of the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.43,0:46:20.43,default,,0,0,0,,This is something I'm drawing with my voice out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.50,0:46:23.50,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.50,0:46:25.50,default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.43,0:46:30.73,default,,0,0,0,,Iku-chan is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.49,0:46:32.15,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.70,0:46:33.70,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.89,0:46:34.89,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.89,0:46:35.89,default,,0,0,0,,Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.89,0:46:36.89,default,,0,0,0,,Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.77,0:46:38.03,default,,0,0,0,,I won't give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.23,0:46:41.37,default,,0,0,0,,There's no sound from the sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.84,0:46:45.10,default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.10,0:46:46.14,default,,0,0,0,,Soshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.14,0:46:48.84,default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way as Ikusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.68,0:46:55.92,default,,0,0,0,,It's really like this in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.97,0:47:10.23,default,,0,0,0,,From here, we'll look at the parts that we thought we shot well and the parts that we don't know why we shot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.33,0:47:13.87,default,,0,0,0,,Moving on. This is a pretty famous scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.87,0:47:20.31,default,,0,0,0,,This is a scene of the members of the principal's school watching over the IKOMA that appeared in the AKB's election.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.51,0:47:21.01,default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.25,0:47:25.65,default,,0,0,0,,I think it's my first time to appear with a reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.76,0:47:29.36,default,,0,0,0,,I was nervous on the other side as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.66,0:47:30.96,default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.89,0:47:34.11,default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.97,0:47:37.97,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.87,0:47:40.83,default,,0,0,0,,Doi-Chu-Yo-I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.01,0:47:44.65,default,,0,0,0,,Final cut shot
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.79,0:47:47.79,default,,0,0,0,,40,000
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.79,0:47:49.79,default,,0,0,0,,40,000
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.38,0:47:53.48,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.25,0:49:11.25,default,,0,0,0,,There is a video of Ikoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.45,0:49:12.05,default,,0,0,0,,The sound is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.80,0:49:14.80,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.69,0:49:14.19,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.24,0:49:15.28,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.95,0:49:19.95,default,,0,0,0,,That's the main thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.26,0:49:20.30,default,,0,0,0,,Get out of Akasaka
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.25,0:49:25.23,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to taste it now, but it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.11,0:49:26.61,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.07,0:49:28.11,default,,0,0,0,,But today...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.73,0:49:29.23,default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.34,0:49:31.32,default,,0,0,0,,I voted for Estelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.77,0:49:35.09,default,,0,0,0,,and Wakatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.52,0:49:36.88,default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.66,0:49:39.64,default,,0,0,0,,Today is the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.09,0:49:42.25,default,,0,0,0,,while eating fruits and granola
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.56,0:49:45.98,default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a monitor infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.17,0:49:46.89,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.55,0:49:48.95,default,,0,0,0,,Now I can go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.57,0:49:50.77,default,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.52,0:49:52.12,default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.25,0:49:54.93,default,,0,0,0,,Good sense of tension
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.36,0:49:57.56,default,,0,0,0,,We went on stage together.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.79,0:49:59.79,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.88,0:50:00.22,default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.45,0:50:02.45,default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.77,0:50:04.97,default,,0,0,0,,This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.92,0:50:07.02,default,,0,0,0,,There are so many
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.67,0:50:10.67,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.44,0:50:10.48,default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.23,0:50:12.89,default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.74,0:50:17.00,default,,0,0,0,,See you at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.31,0:50:18.13,default,,0,0,0,,Maybe next time
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.04,0:50:22.46,default,,0,0,0,,After the event is over, I get in this car and listen to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.81,0:50:24.21,default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.64,0:50:25.94,default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.27,0:50:28.05,default,,0,0,0,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.73,0:50:36.19,default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the ranking is, even if it's low, I think it's expensive for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.89,0:50:38.07,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.27,0:50:39.77,default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's raining,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.90,0:50:42.12,default,,0,0,0,,My activities in AKB48 are
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.23,0:50:44.89,default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.82,0:50:50.36,default,,0,0,0,,Recently, I've been doing a lot of stretching at the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.03,0:50:52.85,default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.21,0:50:54.57,default,,0,0,0,,In my opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.07,0:50:56.31,default,,0,0,0,,I will
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.32,0:51:01.72,default,,0,0,0,,It's not like NATO.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.26,0:51:06.36,default,,0,0,0,,This is a pre-election story.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.59,0:51:08.45,default,,0,0,0,,In this way, IKOMA...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.77,0:51:11.27,default,,0,0,0,,The members can see how hard they work on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.42,0:51:12.60,default,,0,0,0,,I was watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.09,0:51:14.79,default,,0,0,0,,Well, Nogizaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.91,0:51:18.35,default,,0,0,0,,In any of our projects, we use IKOMA together.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.49,0:51:22.83,default,,0,0,0,,We were given a tissue to cheer them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.83,0:51:23.43,default,,0,0,0,,All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.43,0:51:25.57,default,,0,0,0,,All of us, all of the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.89,0:51:28.23,default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was supporting IKOMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.23,0:51:31.79,default,,0,0,0,,All the fans and all the members together.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.13,0:51:36.05,default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the 14th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.89,0:51:42.01,default,,0,0,0,,This is Ikoma after the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.45,0:51:44.39,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.89,0:51:46.49,default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.13,0:51:47.75,default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.97,0:51:49.71,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.17,0:51:52.17,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.56,0:51:55.82,default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.62,0:52:01.48,default,,0,0,0,,I want people to support me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.98,0:52:02.86,default,,0,0,0,,It's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.87,0:52:04.85,default,,0,0,0,,This is Nii's.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.50,0:52:10.58,default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to be able to do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.61,0:52:12.11,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.41,0:52:15.25,default,,0,0,0,,There are so many words that support us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.39,0:52:17.13,default,,0,0,0,,It's very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.69,0:52:19.79,default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
